The paper deals with the optimization of software releases, which is a problem in software engineering (cs.SE). The proposed algorithm involves multilevel reductions and refinements, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also mentions the use of approximate and soft backbones, which are concepts in machine learning (cs.LG) and programming languages (cs.PL).
